00:03:37.759 --> 00:03:39.385
<i>Mislite da ćete poginuti.</i>

00:03:39.553 --> 00:03:40.887
<i>To mislite.</i>

00:03:41.054 --> 00:03:43.472
<i>A onda se, čudesno, to ne dogodi.</i>

00:03:44.141 --> 00:03:45.641
<i>Hvala vam, kapetane.</i>

00:03:45.976 --> 00:03:48.394
<i>Hvala vam, hvala vam.</i>

