Mjerkala me je.
-Gade jedan šarmantni!

00:29:19.174 --> 00:29:20.299
Ahoj.
-Dobrodošli.

00:29:20.467 --> 00:29:21.467
Kako ide?
-Uspjeli ste.

00:29:21.635 --> 00:29:22.885
Da, nego što.
-U redu.

00:29:23.053 --> 00:29:24.220
Hvala vam. Pardon.
-Hvala vam!

00:29:24.388 --> 00:29:26.639
U šestom smo, Jeffe.
-Ne. To je Jimmyjevo.

00:29:26.807 --> 00:29:29.892
