<i>Priredite se!</i>

00:36:09.084 --> 00:36:11.544
<i>Sagnite glave, ostanite sagnuti!</i>

00:36:11.711 --> 00:36:15.464
<i>Cactus 1549, okret nadesno na 2-8-0.
